+ * @param[in]   uIdSubclass Subclass identifier.
+ * @param[in]   dwRefData   ThemeData instance.
+ * @return LRESULT Result of message processing.
+ *
+ * @see DarkMode::setWindowMenuBarSubclass()
+ * @see DarkMode::removeWindowMenuBarSubclass()
